Definition.WordDefinition:
hand-crafted \hand-crafted\ adj. made by hand or by a hand process. Contrasted to {machine-made}. [Narrower terms: {camp-made ; {hand-loomed, handwoven ; {handsewn, handstitched ; {overhand, oversewn )}]
Syn: handmade. [WordNet 1.5]
hand-crafted adj : made by hand or a hand process; "delicate handmade baby dresses" [syn: {handmade}] [ant: {machine-made}]
